<body>
  <h1>Display vs Visibility</h1>
  <div class="box box1">Visible Box</div>
  <div class="box box2 hidden">Hidden Box (visibility: hidden)</div>
  <div class="box box3 none">Removed Box (display: none)</div>
  <p>Note the difference:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>visibility: hidden</strong> - The green box is invisible but still occupies space in the layout.</li>
    <li><strong>display: none</strong> - The red box is completely removed from the document flow, so it does not occupy space.</li>
  </ul>
</body>
